					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220520014316/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/Mic">Michaeas</a></li>
					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220520014316/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/Nah">Nahum</a></li>
